    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri'; font-size: 11pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {className: a3; text-indent: 48px;}\n.html-preview .a4 td {border: 1px solid #000;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 311.0027700831px;\">\n<p></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 311.0027700831px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Фуқаролик ишлари бўйича</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#2}Ариза берилган фуқаролик ишлари бўйича суд номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">га</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Ариза берган шахснинг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Ариза берган шахснинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">дан</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 311.0027700831px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 311.0027700831px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 3=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 311.0027700831px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 377.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">А<span class=\"leading\"></span>Р И З А</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">(Илтимосномани қайтариб олиш тўғрисида)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Фуқаролик ишлари бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Ишни кўриб чиқаётган фуқаролик ишлар бўйича суд номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> судида </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Иш бўйича даъвогарнинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">нинг</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">менга нисбатан </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Иш бўйича даъвонинг мазмуни</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> тўғрисидаги даъво аризаси юзасидан фуқаролик иши кўрилмоқда.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Суд томонидан ишни очиқ суд мажлисидан кўриш </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Суд мажлиси тайинланган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">кунига тайинланган.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Мазкур фуқаролик иши юзасидан мен янги далилларни талаб қилиб олиш тўғрисидаги илтимоснома билан мурожаат қилганман.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Лекин, мен талаб қилиб олинишини сўраган далиллар ишни кўриш вақтида иш бўйича учинчи шахс </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Иш бўйича учинчи шахснинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> томонидан тақдим этилди.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Шу сабабли, мени илтимосномамни муҳокама қилишга эҳтиёж қолмаган деб ҳисоблайман.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Юқоридагиларга кўра ҳамда Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик процессуал кодексининг 40, 44, 219-моддаларига асосланиб, </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 14pt; margin-bottom: 14.4pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">СЎРАЙМАН:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Менинг янги далилларни талаб қилиб олиш тўғрисидаги илтимосномамни қайтаришингизни.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Аризага илова қилинаётган ҳужжатлар:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">1. Илтимоснома нусхаси</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Ариза берган шахснинг Ф.И.О.си</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">____________</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;\">(имзо)</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Ариза берилган сана</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</div></div>",
